These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, almond-milk, fanta, soy-milk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, april, october, march
There 4 different types of food: onion, garlic, peas, spinach
4 different games are played: chess, billiard, poker, go
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cricket, biathlon, rugby
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 2. the person eating spinach is between the person drinking cola and the person who's sport is rugby##2
 3. the person playing chess is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 4. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 5. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person drinking cola and the person eating peas##2
 6. the person playing go is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 7. the person who's sport is cricket is the person drinking fanta##1
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
10. the person eating onion is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| Beverage           | fanta | cola   | soy-milk | almond-milk |
| Birthday   | january      | april | october              | march |
| Food   | onion       | garlic     | spinach               | peas    |
| Game           | billiard        | poker     | go           | chess       |
| Sport     | cricket | biathlon     | climbing                | rugby      |

