.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, filmmaking, reading, camping
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, yellow, azure, ivory
House: tower, townhouse, colonial, modern
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, tiparillo, bongani, oliveros
City: venice, colone, london, nizza
 1. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 2. the tower house is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 3. the person who likes yellow is between the person who's hobby is reading and the tiparillo-smoker##2
 4. the modern house is the person traveling to venice##1
 5. the bongani-smoker is the person who likes yellow##1
 6. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
 7. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 8. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
 9. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
10. the person who likes azure is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
11. the person traveling to venice is the person who's hobby is reading##1
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who likes azure##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Hobby          | reading       | filmmaking      | card-games      | camping      |
| Color           | ivory | yellow | azure | purple |
| House   | modern          | townhouse       | colonial            | tower      |
| Cigar           | dunhill            | bongani    | tiparillo           | oliveros       |
| City         | venice        | colone    | london         | nizza  |

