 4. the person driving the skateboard is the person who likes light-blue##1
 5. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 6. the person traveling to miami is between the person playing bridge and the person who likes amber##2
 7. the designer is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 8. the person traveling to hannover is the person who likes black##1
 9. the designer is the person driving the jet-ski##1
10. the paramedic is on the far left##1
11. the paramedic is the person who likes amber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
