.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, july, june, january
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, oliveros, swisher, prince
4 different pets are kept: hamster, goat, goldfish, chinchilla
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, mystery, adventure, epic
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, chinese, russian, spanish
 1. the russian is the chaman-smoker##1
 2. the chinese is between the owner of the hamster and the owner of the goat##2
 3. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is the person watching spy movies##1
 5. the owner of the goat is between the person watching spy movies and the nigerian##2
 6. the person watching epic movies is on the far left##1
 7. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is the spanish##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is between the chinese and the owner of the goldfish##2
10. the prince-smoker is on the far left##1
11. the oliveros-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Birthday      | january     | july | june    | october          |
| Cigar          | prince | chaman     | swisher | oliveros         |
| Pet   | goldfish    | goat       | chinchilla         | hamster        |
| Movie-Genre         | epic  | mystery     | spy     | adventure |
| Nationality     | nigerian     | russian      | chinese   | spanish          |

