 3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 4. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 5. the person who likes orange is on the far right##1
 6. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 9. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
10. the person who likes emerald is between the person who likes light-blue and the owner of the rat##2
11. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
12. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
