There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, amber, grey, ivory
City: paris, edinburgh, venice, miami
 1. the fan hip-hop is on the right of the fan country##1
 2. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 3. the fan pop is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 6. the person who likes ivory is the fan pop##1
 7. the person who likes blood-red is the fan country##1
 8. the fan hip-hop is between the fan pop and the person who's birthday is in february##2
 9. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left##1
10. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person watching western movies##2
11. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Birthday          | february       | october       | may | march    |
| Movie-Genre         | scientific     | time-travel | western | sports     |
| Music-Genre           | country        | hip-hop    | pop  | electronic |
| Color   | blood-red      | grey      | ivory     | amber     |
| City         | miami | venice      | edinburgh    | paris |

