 2. the person who growsdahlia is between the person who likes chestnut and the person playing poker##2
 3. the person who likes coral is between the wooden house and the colonial house##2
 4. the person playing snooker is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 5. the person who growszinnia is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 6. the person who likes coral is the farmhouse house##1
 7. the person playing scrabble is the wooden house##1
 8. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 9. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
10. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who growsmonopolying##1
11. the person who growsmonopolying is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person playing scrabble##2
12. the person who growsdahlia is between the person playing snooker and the farmhouse house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |    3     |     4      |
| House      | colonial      | farmhouse         | wooden | art-deco      |
| Birthday           | november | january | september | february     |
| Color   | amber         | coral          | white  | chestnut |
| Flower         | zinnia        | monopolying  | dahlia | tulip   |
| Game     | monopoly    | poker         | scrabble     | snooker     |

