.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-20::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, dog, pony, bird
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, bolivar, swisher, baccarat
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, blueberry, onion, cauliflower
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, purple, chestnut, emerald
House: townhouse, gothic-revival, palace, wooden
 1. the baccarat-smoker is the person eating blueberry##1
 2. the wooden house is between the person eating cauliflower and the person who likes turquise##2
 3. the gothic-revival house is between the person who likes purple and the palace house##2
 4. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 5. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
 6. the person who likes purple is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 7. the owner of the dog is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 8. the swisher-smoker is the person who likes chestnut##1
 9. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the palace house##1
10. the owner of the turtle is the person eating cabbage##1
11. the person eating cabbage is the person who likes emerald##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Pet         | pony  | dog | bird | turtle |
| Cigar   | baccarat      | bolivar   | swisher      | tiparillo    |
| Food   | blueberry  | onion | cauliflower        | cabbage     |
| Color         | turquise  | purple  | chestnut     | emerald      |
| House     | townhouse | wooden      | gothic-revival   | palace       |

 